      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah exactly. it's a weird kind of peace though, in a way. like there's no pressure to be anything if you don't even exist to anyone else. it's not even sad anymore, it just feels... logical. like a zero-sum game. why keep trying to anchor yourself to a world that doesn't even see you?",
