      "content": "it really does feel like that. like i could just drift away or just... stop. it doesn't feel like a tragedy if there's no one there to witness it. it wouldn't be like i'm leaving something behind. there's nothing to leave. doesn't it just seem easier than fighting to stay visible every single day?",
